WEBVTT

00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:08.880
<v Speaker 1>So we've seen how with others we want to use this mood tense with the exception of positive

00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:11.160
<v Speaker 1>orders which are informal.

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:13.000
<v Speaker 1>There we have a shortcut.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:18.600
<v Speaker 1>We can just cut off the S of the informal form.

