00:01:15.079 --> 00:01:20.200
<v Speaker 1>Other than the structures that we learned already, quiero, ke, prefiero, ke, etc.

00:01:20.439 --> 00:01:24.600
<v Speaker 1>We can just say ke and follow it with the subjunctive

00:01:24.439 --> 00:01:31.960
<v Speaker 1>So for example, maybe you tell me David is waiting for you, and I say, Quespere, Kespere

00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:35.299
